node.text: Nothing in this life comes easy. In order to achieve your goals, you must make certain sacrifices - spend your energy, time, limit yourself in something. Sometimes there are times when you want to give up everything and give up your dream. At such moments, remember how much you will gain if you go further and how much you will lose if you give up. The price of success is usually less than the price of failure.ü§ûüèºüòª

‚ÄúDo you know what happiness means?‚Äù This is not something that you should expect all your life, for happiness it is not necessary to earn millions and succeed in all areas of life. Happiness is when you do not expect anyone, and they come and lighten your mood from minus infinity to the exact opposite. Happiness is when a handwritten note with warm words warms you more than two blankets and a blanket. Happiness is when those with whom I have not talked for months are sincerely interested in your well-being. Happiness is when life gives you all the chances and you use them one hundred percent. Appreciate those near you. Any difficulties present us with a lesson, open our eyes and provide food for thought. Take a look around. Who asks every day how are you? Who, knowing that you are in a bad mood, will try to lift you and calm you down? Who can chat with you for hours on end? Remember someone? Hug him tight and appreciate!üòªüññüèº
